A revenge thriller featuring a femme fatale who uses her medical knowledge to heal or hurt.
She was reborn in the body of a mistreated young noble lady. Surrounded by greedy, calculating relatives? No big deal! Her needles will put them in line! Face marred by scars and fingers broken? A piece of cake! With her medical skills, she'll soon restore her beauty and strength! Arrogant and cold-blooded, he's the most powerful man in the court of the Xia dynasty, yet he will fall in love with her at first sight…
(Source: Webcomics)
Action, Adventure, Drama, Fantasy, Horror, Psychological

Only I can see the future in this deadly game. Yoon-Jae leads an empty life after his wife and daughter are brutally murdered. One day, his journal reveals one mysterious sentence: “You can see them again.” Yoon-Jae is pulled into a parallel universe where everyone is a player in a lethal game, and the final survivor will be granted any wish. Desperate to be reunited with his family, will Yoon-Jae succeed in fighting his way in this hellish world to be the last one standing?
(Source: Manta)
